{"title":"仰望国旗","authors":["蔡玉环"],"dates":[{"year":2000,"month":10,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰望国旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔡玉环"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金秋时节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳映衬下的国旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红艳如沸腾的血液"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿烂地融进我的诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天我用肺腑的真诚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰望国旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿如仰望一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族智慧的精华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰望一个国家超越时空的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不朽真理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五颗金黄的星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耀亮一片热土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热土上有硝烟弥漫的重彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有铁蹄枪刺带响的寒风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有炮火弹片烧灼的伤痕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更有共和国卫士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铮铮的誓言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我用全身心的虔诚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰望国旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经过血与火的洗礼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的国旗愈发鲜艳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它搏动着亿万人民的心脉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在锦绣神州"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临风招展着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新世纪的风采"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}